Paper: hep-th/9704093

Date: 1997-04-11

Title: Pasti-Sorokin-Tonin Actions in the Presence of Sources

Authors: R. Medina, N. Berkovits

Comments: 6 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D56 (1997) 6388-6390

Pasti, Sorokin and Tonin have recently constructed manifestlyLorentz-invariant actions for self-dual field strengths and for Maxwell fieldswith manifest electromagnetic duality. Using the method of Deser, Gomberoff,Henneaux and Teitelboim, we generalize these actions in the presence ofsources.